Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.86,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.54,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.76,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0}'s first chapter was #1 in the rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.66,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,We're getting closer to our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.88,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Everything will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:26.08,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.32,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:01:01.98,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Hey, if I could be with you right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:11.34,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Then I could keep my voice from fading
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:18.08,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,The goals I've set for myself seem too high to reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:22.50,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,and I feel like I've lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:32.10,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I'm relying on a broken compass and hiding in someone's shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:43.46,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,If we keep letting go of what we have to find something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:53.28,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,then I'm convinced we can never grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:59.08,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.00,Title,sign,0,0,250,,Willpower and Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.43,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.77,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I'm going to make {\i1}+Natural{\i0} into {\i1}Jack{\i0}'s #1...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.18,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,No... Japan's #1 manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:14.08,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I won't lose to {\i1}PCP{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:16.04,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:19.22,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,We have an anime starting in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.63,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Oh, thats right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.36,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:23.66,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:28.10,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,The heroine, Mimiya Sayano,\Nmakes her appearence in episode 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:32.17,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,These are the four best applicants for the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:39.12,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,I'll have Niizuma-kun to listen\Nto a few samples, and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.51,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,This Azuki Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:43.64,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I went to middle school with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.00,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Eh!? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.47,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.06,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,This girl... is Mashiro's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.66,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.40,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:55.42,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,She visited him in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.57,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Azuki Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.98,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Mashiro Moritaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.34,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Takagi Akito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.49,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.04,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,First place for the first chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.58,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Off to a good start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.30,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.41,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,After this we'll have to work hard to keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.54,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:23.12,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,We need to strengthen our characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.44,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But... Is it too much for her to be good at sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.10,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,For a heroine thats fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.32,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.28,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.14,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,It's from Miura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.18,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Hey Mashiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:41.30,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Were you really in middle school with Azuki Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:41.94,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:45.76,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Just how awesome was your class anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.50,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,You two and Akina-kun are writing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.54,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,And Azuki is a voice actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.92,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,I must admit I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.76,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.42,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Why are you asking about Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.96,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Because Miho-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:01.52,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Is auditioning to be Sayano in {\i1}+Natural{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:04.84,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,What?! The part of Sayano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.84,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,What. You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.93,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,The audition is this next Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.57,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Wish her luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.50,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.42,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Azuki in {\i1}+Natural{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.24,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.40,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.14,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.00,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,You were talking about Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:20.96,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:24.55,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Why would Miura-san ask\Nabout Miho on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.24,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Azuki is auditioning for the\Nrole of Sayano in {\i1}+Natural{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.54,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Sayano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.26,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,This girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.00,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,The heroine of {\i1}+Natural{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:33.78,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.74,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Iwase and Niizuma's manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.98,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,She has an audition next Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.60,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,So why did Miura-san call?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.41,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.30,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,He's the editor for {\i1}+Natural{\i0} now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.92,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,He was just surprised to learn\Nthat she is a voice actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.14,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Why would Miho apply for this role?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:50.24,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,She needs to play Annojo Mai when {\i1}PCP{\i0} gets an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.42,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Sayano doesn't show up until later in the series,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.98,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But there are no other major female characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.80,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,And she eventually becomes the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.70,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,But Miho is your heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.16,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,She can't do any others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.78,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,And the manga is by your rivals, Niizuma and Iwase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.82,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,It isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.61,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Mashiro, you have to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.45,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.06,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,This is a big role.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:20.50,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,But she needs to be the heroine in your story...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.83,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,In order for your dream to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.46,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Work is work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.52,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,My job is to write manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.42,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Azuki is working hard to become a voice actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:34.12,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,If that means playing a role in\NIwase and Niizuma's anime, {\i1}+Natural{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.10,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.30,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.70,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,That isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.52,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Kaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.44,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.72,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,It's not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.60,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Thats terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.12,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,I'm just thinking of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.54,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.72,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But it's not our place to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.04,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:00.04,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,You can't say that kind of thing in front of Saiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:00.98,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:04.72,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he doesn't want\Nher to take that part either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:10.43,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But it's Azuki's choice so he won't stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.48,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.26,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Because he's stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.84,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.31,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,I guess I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.51,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Sometimes he has trouble saying what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.60,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Azuki too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.98,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.69,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Why did she choose that role anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.78,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.18,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,"I can't be in Mashiro's rival's anime",
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.40,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Is what I would expect her to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.66,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But she isn't that type.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.54,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.57,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,It's work so she'll try her hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:40.71,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,It's her job so it's her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:43.26,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Let's go see her tomorrow and talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:44.82,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.88,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,Welcome you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.48,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.72,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Sorry to come on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.76,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.90,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,There's so much I want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:56.08,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.62,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,A-ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.14,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.73,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,How did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:05.70,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,We happened to hear it\Nfrom the editor of {\i1}+Natural{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.46,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Why did you apply for the role?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.35,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,My boss is the one who\Nsubmitted the application.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.54,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.24,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Well, you got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:13.98,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.52,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,When is the audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.70,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,On Saturday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.62,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,At 1pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:19.49,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.42,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Near Shibuya station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.84,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.98,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,I don't think you should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.92,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,What if you actually get the role?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:30.21,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,If you get the role of Sayano...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.26,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,And our manga gets an anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.50,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:38.02,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,That would be the same\Nvoice actor for two {\i1}Jack{\i0} series.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:42.85,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,They probably wouldn't let you\Ndo ours in addition to {\i1}+Natural{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.31,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,What did Mashiro say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.50,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,As you might expect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.86,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,"It's Miho's job so Miho should decide"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.78,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.16,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I know him so I understand the way he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.54,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But I don't want you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.90,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:02.20,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee that we\Nwill get an anime right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:06.17,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But you're supposed to be\Nthe heroine for our story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.38,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,{\i1}+Natural{\i0} isn't the only anime out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.22,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,It isn't right to do something that will\Nkeep your dreams from coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.72,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Don't be stubborn!\NBe honest with yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:14.84,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Kaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:18.46,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,I know Mashiro would be happy if\Nyou said that you wouldn't audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.47,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.42,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,If you tell him that I'm sure he'll be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:26.14,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,And wouldn't you be happy if\Nhe told you not to audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:26.81,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.74,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,You're both so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:33.00,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Anyway, you should just avoid\Ndoing any {\i1}Jack{\i0} heroine parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.03,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:38.24,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko is right to say that\Nyour job is your own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.24,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:43.94,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I don't want you to audition if it's\Nonly because he didn't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.34,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,...Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.84,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'll email him today and ask him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.64,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:55.34,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,But you already know\Nwhat his answer will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.04,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Kaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.57,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,This is all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.76,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,It's up to Azuki and Saiko now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.54,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.70,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:03.43,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,But this doesn't solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.46,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.82,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.34,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,See you later Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.02,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Azuki as Sayano...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.72,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.79,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,...Azuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.20,Dialogue,text,0,0,0,,Are we too stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.21,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,...Are we ... too stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.46,Dialogue,text,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:49.08,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.88,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,First page is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.88,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.86,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Kaya-chan! Please quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.32,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.10,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,I'm trying to motivate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.00,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,You're making it hard to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.39,Dialogue,helper,0,0,0,,Mashiro-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.34,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.95,Dialogue,helper,0,0,0,,This panel on the third page...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:11.06,Dialogue,helper,0,0,0,,Something about the angle\Njust doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.30,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Let me have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.63,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.64,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I'll fix it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:21.00,Dialogue,bandana,0,0,0,,Moriya-san is the same as ever eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:21.62,Dialogue,blonde,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:23.68,Dialogue,blonde,0,0,0,,I think something is up this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:24.48,Dialogue,bandana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:29.12,Dialogue,blonde,0,0,0,,I can fix the mistakes I find as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.67,Dialogue,blonde,0,0,0,,But there are more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.68,Dialogue,bandana,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:32.30,Dialogue,blonde,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:37.24,Dialogue,blonde,0,0,0,,Hopefully we can fix everything before we turn in the manuscript tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.87,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} is in second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:41.90,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crow{\i0} is in third.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.90,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,{\i1}+Natural{\i0} is in fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.00,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.48,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,Let's meet today at 6pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:47.58,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.42,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,{\i1}+Natural{\i0}'s anime starts next month,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.43,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,So we'd better not relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.50,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Second place is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.07,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,It's a good response.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.46,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.99,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,But if Azuki plays Sayano in {\i1}+Natural{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.84,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Is that really ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.58,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,The audition is tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.81,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.40,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh that's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.88,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Let's keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.27,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,You forgot to close the copier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.51,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Shoot... I wasted a sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.26,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:19.52,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I... told Azuki not to audition if she was\Nonly doing it because you didn't stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.42,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:25.20,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I know it's not my place... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.79,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,No... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.14,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,The dialogue here is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:36.90,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,But what's wrong Mashiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:40.72,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,Your art hasn't but up to its usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.38,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Hattori-san! Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.33,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.39,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I'll make corrections now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.34,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,I would like to say yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:51.39,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,But I promised I would bring the\Nmanuscript to a meeting in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.74,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,So this should be good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:54.56,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.18,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I can do it in two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.18,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Let me have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.19,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.02,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I'll help too... what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:03.36,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,No, your dialogue is already fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.27,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Fixing this is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.18,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,If I can't do that I'm not a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.54,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:20.64,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Azuki is working so hard for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.02,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,It isn't stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.02,Text,text,0,0,0,,Are we too stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.82,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I respect her and trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.14,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,If she doesn't back down I won't stop her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:33.83,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,But was Shujin right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.14,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Am I just forcing the decision onto her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.06,Dialogue,text,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.10,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:46.70,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,That line was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.03,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Well, Niizuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.74,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Did anyone stand out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.32,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Everyone did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.91,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,It's hard to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.70,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Then, Azuki Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.59,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,I don't think we should choose Azuki Miho-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.36,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Eh?! Miho is no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.46,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,No good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.04,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,She's Mashiro-sensei's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:10.18,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,I don't think he and Takagi-sensei would\Nlike it very much if she were in our anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.43,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.23,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,But she is a voice actor anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:18.48,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Anyway don't mention that tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.07,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.62,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Well good luck with the auditions tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:24.53,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:27.30,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,Good luck Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.16,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.94,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Well, I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.54,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.71,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.94,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,This might be unnessesary,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:40.12,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,But It's important to follow\Nyour heart when you're uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.92,Dialogue,mom,0,0,0,,Being stubborn doesn't help anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.68,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.92,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,The audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.01,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Thats today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.10,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.98,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,What will Miho do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.22,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I told you not to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.44,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.32,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,The audition is at 1pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.28,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.53,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.16,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.96,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'll definitely become a voice\Nactor and be in your anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.18,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,It's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.68,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.13,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'll wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.04,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.76,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I believe in you Mashiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.20,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Make our dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:41.77,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Ah! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.32,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Aren't we early?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.78,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Let's audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.35,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.34,Dialogue,receptionist,0,0,0,,Good... day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.02,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Miura-san, what floor is it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.20,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.60,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,The second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.72,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.02,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.00,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:12.80,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,What could that pen name mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.68,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,"A" from Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.35,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,"Shiro" from Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.06,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,"Gi" from Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.31,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,And "our dreams will come true"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.52,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,It means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.56,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Their manga will get an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.03,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,And I will play the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.86,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,That is our dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:34.06,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,OHO! What a fantastic dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.26,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Is that why they got into manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:36.83,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.28,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I came here today to decline the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.80,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,You must be joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.50,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Hearing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.84,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Really makes me want to use you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:52.40,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I'll make Sayano into the perfect heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:55.52,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,If you turn down the role\Nfor personal reasons like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.38,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.78,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Consider yourself warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.02,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.18,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Are all women this scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:04.88,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:05.98,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.82,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.11,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Mashiro-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.22,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.48,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Go where??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.33,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Let's just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.48,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.74,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:24.48,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.46,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.64,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Mashiro-sensei is super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.42,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.46,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,I'll reject Miho-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.36,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,And I won't let anybody complain about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.54,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Thank you Niizuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:35.88,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.90,Dialogue,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Love wins again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.22,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.64,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'm happy though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.48,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Even though I interfered with your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.04,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I had gone there today\Nto turn down the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.72,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,We both came to the same conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.00,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,We're still on the same page.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.58,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.32,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,You held my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.54,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.86,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Sorry... I let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.46,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I feel like I can rely on you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:24.84,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Can't you always?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:29.52,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Well if it's not about manga\Nyou can be unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.76,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,And you're stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.46,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,So are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:39.04,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,We may be stubborn but\Nwe're even bad at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:41.72,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,How many times have we broken our\Npromise to not see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.30,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,It was an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.75,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.70,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'm very disappointed in you Mashiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:51.76,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't want to hold hands\Nuntil our dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.88,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,You really are the most\Nstubborn guy I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.18,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.08,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Miura-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:02.50,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I would like to meet with\Nyou after the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.66,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:04.64,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Y-yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.52,Dialogue,niizuma,0,0,0,,Quickly! Begin the auditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.80,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,From Shinjuku I need to\Ntake the Saikyo Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.96,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,And you take the Chuo Line right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:13.94,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.96,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,We've only had five minutes together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.06,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Can I go with you to Yakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.84,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,B-but... I have to work on the\Nmanuscript when I bet back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.47,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I'll just ride with you to Yakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.34,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Then I'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.50,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:34.18,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Azuki-san is so forward today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.69,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Is it because I held her hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:39.74,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's ride together to Yakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.02,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,You're really funny today Mashiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.68,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.32,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,We're supposed to stay away from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.78,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,But this keeps happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:02.91,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I'm happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.98,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,It's the next station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.10,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,We've been together for 40 minutes already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.48,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,I was so happy...\Nit all flew by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.48,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.02,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.56,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Next time we see each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.40,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Let's kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.60,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,What are you saying Azuki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.48,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Is this all because I held her hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.98,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,But how does that lead to kissing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.52,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,This isn't like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:40.02,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,So let's not meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.94,Dialogue,azuki,0,0,0,,Until our dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.06,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,...When our dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.14,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,That's just like Azuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:04.34,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,He can't be like that just from seeing her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.00,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,I told you, he's just happy\Nshe didn't audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.18,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Something else must have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.62,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.18,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.76,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.56,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.30,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.33,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.68,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Did something happen\Nbetween you and Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.84,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,I can see it on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.98,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Eh? My face! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:26.78,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Tell us what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.38,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Oh nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.46,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Liar! I bet you kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.66,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Kiss? No way! We didn't kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.15,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.34,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,Hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:41.10,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,All you did was hold hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.22,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,That is just like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.16,Dialogue,kaya,0,0,0,,What are you, in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:48.72,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Shut up! We're just taking it slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.00,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Azuki Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.38,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I won't forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:54.68,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I'll make sure she regrets\Nleaving my audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.08,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,She'll never have work\Nas a voice actor again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.96,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,I'll drag Ashirogi Muto down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.20,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.04,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Now spill all of your ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.34,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,You know Ashirogi-kun\Nisn't just fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:08.95,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,They're very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.32,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,You're on their side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.72,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you helped\Nthem make {\i1}PCP{\i0} didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.58,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}+Natural{\i0}'s editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:20.42,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,I believe in your talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.28,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:28.64,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Authors should compete with their content.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.20,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,That's the best help I can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.16,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Then give me another idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:37.44,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Hattori would have done\Na much better job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.98,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,Well! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.12,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Ok... Where did we leave off last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.94,Dialogue,iwase,0,0,0,,You mean you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.18,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.87,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0}'s third chapter is in fifth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.72,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,{\i1}+Natural{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:53.00,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:57.42,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,As long as we're above {\i1}PCP{\i0}\Nthat should keep Akina happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.28,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,Hattori, whats wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.30,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0}'s third chapter did great right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.86,Dialogue,miura,0,0,0,,You should hurry up and tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.72,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,Yeah... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.05,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,Chapter three is in fifth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.49,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,Normally that would be great...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:13.64,Dialogue,manager,0,0,0,,They have six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.90,Dialogue,manager,0,0,0,,We'll see how it goes until chapter 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:19.85,Dialogue,manager,0,0,0,,If their rating is low\Nby the seventh chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.50,Dialogue,manager,0,0,0,,I won't hesitate to cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:24.60,Dialogue,manager,0,0,0,,After 25 chapters,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:27.06,Dialogue,manager,0,0,0,,If it hasn't surpassed {\i1}Crow{\i0} and {\i1}+Natural{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:28.44,Dialogue,manager,0,0,0,,It will be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:31.44,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:35.14,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,At this rate they won't surpass {\i1}+Natural{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.96,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,We have to keep the rating up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.38,Dialogue,hattori,0,0,0,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:58.02,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,When I struggle toward my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:02.58,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Those are the moments I love the most
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:07.16,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I can feel our bond and will to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:11.80,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Our views overlap and electrify us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:16.42,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Let's improve ourselves, become what we should be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:21.46,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,You can see the future in our path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:26.50,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,My comrades don't agree with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:34.28,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Our pride clashes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:42.58,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I can't let it go, I'll follow my heart from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:44.88,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I'm prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:49.32,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I'll charge right in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:52.44,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,Unstoppable Pride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:24:00.84,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,There's no other choice, this is what I love and this is what I'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:05.88,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,I don't know what tomorrow will bring
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:08.84,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,But I know once again (just to get by),
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:11.50,Karaoke,karaoke,0,0,0,,We'll do our best
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:16.90,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,Our new serialization has finally started!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:18.64,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,But we have some tough conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:22.18,Dialogue,takagi,0,0,0,,With our rivals doing their\Nbest, can we pull through?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.18,0:24:24.18,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,Next: Every Night and Unite.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:27.16,Dialogue,mashiro,0,0,0,,We'll have to work hard to reach our dreams!
